371
00:19:39,567 --> 00:19:42,733
Stop saying you're sorry.

372
00:19:42,733 --> 00:19:45,132
You can be there for me from now on.

373
00:19:45,133 --> 00:19:48,065
See me get married, have kids,

374
00:19:48,066 --> 00:19:51,531
