375
00:19:51,532 --> 00:19:53,067
Okay?

376
00:19:53,099 --> 00:19:55,199
Okay.

377
00:19:55,233 --> 00:19:57,299
Are you seeing anyone?

378
00:19:57,300 --> 00:19:58,799
What?

379
00:20:00,199 --> 00:20:01,700
There is someone, isn't there?

380
00:20:01,700 --> 00:20:03,400
Right?

381
00:20:04,734 --> 00:20:06,399
You've met him once.

382
00:20:06,400 --> 00:20:08,666
