383
00:20:08,666 --> 00:20:10,332
It's the CEO.

384
00:20:10,333 --> 00:20:11,933
What?

385
00:20:11,933 --> 00:20:13,832
The CEO of your magazine?

386
00:20:13,833 --> 00:20:15,431
Oh, my goodness!

387
00:20:15,432 --> 00:20:17,566
He seemed like such a nice person.

388
00:20:17,567 --> 00:20:20,165
He's handsome and competent.

389
00:20:20,166 --> 00:20:23,999
Oh, my goodness! I'm so happy for you!

390
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:27,133
I guess your mother knows him well.

391
00:20:27,166 --> 00:20:29,065
I'm curious to know who he is.

392
00:20:29,066 --> 00:20:30,867
Want to see a picture?

393
00:20:33,432 --> 00:20:35,166
Handsome, right?

394
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:45,366
Is this man's name Yoo Ja Sung?

395
00:20:45,366 --> 00:20:47,000
What?

396
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:49,165
How do you know Ja Sung?

397
00:20:49,166 --> 00:20:50,900
Indeed.

398
00:20:51,599 --> 00:20:53,565
Do you know him?

399
00:21:03,033 --> 00:21:05,065
