00:21:05,066 --> 00:21:07,633
It's all about taking memorable pictures.

401
00:21:07,633 --> 00:21:08,698
So?

402
00:21:08,699 --> 00:21:11,300
Have you got the hang of it?

403
00:21:11,300 --> 00:21:15,899
With skills like this, you'll never get to take memorable photos with Editor Na.

404
00:21:15,933 --> 00:21:18,232
This selfie stick...

405
00:21:18,233 --> 00:21:19,865
